{"id":63919,"date":"2021-11-14T11:21:13","date_gmt":"2021-11-14T10:21:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/?p=63919"},"modified":"2022-06-27T13:46:28","modified_gmt":"2022-06-27T11:46:28","slug":"roussillon-le-sentier-des-ocres","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/roussillon-le-sentier-des-ocres\/","title":{"rendered":"Visit Roussillon and Le Sentier des Ocres (Canyon)"},"content":{"rendered":"<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-about-roussillon-and-its-le-sentier-des-ocres-trail\">About Roussillon and its Le Sentier des Ocres Trail<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The beauty of Roussillon is hard to beat! The village sits high on top of a ridge with the deep canyon below. The canyon was once a quarry for ochre, which is a natural clay that is found in the valley and rocks close to the village. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120420\/roussillon2-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"roussillon french houses\"><\/noscript><img width=\"225\" height=\"338\" alt=\"roussillon french houses\" class=\"wp-image-68344 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120420\/roussillon2-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120420\/roussillon2-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120420\/roussillon2-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120420\/roussillon2-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120420\/roussillon2-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltino