oads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-225x338.jpg 225w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-720x1080.jpg 720w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-960x1440.jpg 960w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-600x900.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13.jpg 1280w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133828\/roussillon13-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-1080x721.jpg\" alt=\"Le Sentier des Ocres\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"Le Sentier des Ocres\" class=\"wp-image-68380 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133806\/roussillon11-1080x721.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The varying colors of ochre made it the perfect material to use for the houses here. As a result, everywhere you look in Roussillon is as colorful as an artist&#x2019;s palette, with houses ranging from terracotta oranges to dusky pinks, warm yellows, and deep reds. Each house is complemented by colorful shutters and painted doorways. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>All of this, plus the clear blue summer sky and bright green trees, make Roussillon&#x2019;s scenery truly magical.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/france\/french-riviera-travel-guide\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">French Riviera Guide: 12 days in the South of France<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2 id=\"h-visiting-le-sentier-des-ocres-the-canyon\">Visiting Le Sentier des Ocres (The Canyon)<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Le Sentier des Ocres (The Canyon) is the former ochre mine next to Roussillon. The canyon is incredibly deep as it was mined for ochre (a natural clay) for many years. Now the valley has been turned into a trail for visitors, worming among the waves and ridges of the cliffs. Most impressive of all is the amazing variety of colors of the clay you&#x2019;ll see on the pathway, moving from deep reds to golden yellows and dark browns. At times, it&#x2019;s hard to believe you&#x2019;re in France!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9.jpg\" alt=\"Le Sentier des Ocres Trail roussillon\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Le Sentier des Ocres Trail roussillon\" class=\"wp-image-68371 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-600x750.jpg 600w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11123441\/roussillon9.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>There are many myths about the red color of the clay that can be found here. One of the dramatic legends is that it&#x2019;s the blood of Lady Sermond who jumped off the cliffs after an altercation with her jealous husband.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>These stories make for some interesting discussions as you walk among the vivid colors and see the incredible views from the trail!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-68382 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133817\/roussillon12-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-540x810.jpg\" alt=\"Le Sentier des Ocres france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"Le Sentier des Ocres france\" class=\"wp-image-68378 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 540px) 100vw, 540px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-600x899.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10.jpg 1281w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-20x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11133754\/roussillon10-540x810.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>Routes and Opening Times<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are two different routes you can take at &#x2018;Le Sentier des Ocres&#x2019;. The longer route is just around an hour, and the shorter one is approximately 30 minutes.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--attractions \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Entry fee:<\/strong> 2.50 EUR<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Opening times:<\/strong> Every day from Mid February &#x2013; December. In the summer months, the trail is open from 9 AM &#x2013; 7.30 PM.&#xA0; Please note that the opening hours in the winter vary and are much shorter.<\/p>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/63919&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11145121\/roussillon-france4.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11145121\/roussillon-france4-17x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/11\/11145121\/roussillon-france4-338x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Visit Roussillon and Le Sentier des Ocres (Canyon)\" height=\"600\" width=\"338\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h2>Roussillon village in France<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The village is tiny, so it won&#x2019;t take long to walk around. Start in the main square, Place de la Marie, and enjoy a cup of coffee in one of the restaurants while people watch the locals go about their day-to-day errands. After, walk in the maze of narrow streets before finding your way to the beautiful church, Eglise Saint Michel. This charming church has a 19th-century clock tower with bells and is a lovely spot to sit down and take in the sights and sounds of Roussillon, France.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120534\/roussillon8.jpg\" alt=\"roussillon france village\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"roussillon france village\" class=\"wp-image-68357 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/1112