rough Sunny Cars, all insurances are included, no surprises when collecting your car. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sunnycars-en-france\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your local rental car here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p>However, If you&#x2019;re traveling by train, get off at station &#x2018;Cavaillon&#x2019;. From here, it&#x2019;s possible to take a public bus to Roussillon.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120458\/roussillon5.jpg\" alt=\"roussillon france\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"roussillon france\" class=\"wp-image-68351 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120458\/roussillon5.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120458\/roussillon5-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120458\/roussillon5-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120458\/roussillon5-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120458\/roussillon5-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120458\/roussillon5-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120458\/roussillon5-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120458\/roussillon5-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120458\/roussillon5-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/11120458\/roussillon5-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/up